## Component Interaction Flow

### 1. Device Control Flow
Mobile App → REST API → Device Service → MQTT Broker → ESP32 → Hardware ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ User Validate & Update Publish to Subscribe Execute Initiates Process Database Topic & Execute Action Action Request Update Control Command (Relay/PWM) ↓ Confirmation Feedback ← ← ← WebSocket/Push

Code

### 2. Real-time Monitoring Flow
Hardware Sensors → ESP32 → MQTT Publish → Backend Service → Cache Update ↓ ↓ ↓ Process Data Store in DB Broadcast to Connected Clients ↓ Alert/Notification Service (WhatsApp, Email, Push)

Code

### 3. Order Processing Flow
POS System → REST API → Order Service → Job Queue → Inventory Check ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ New Order Validate & Create Enqueue for AI Forecast Received Store Order Record Processing & Stock Check ↓ ↓ ↓ WebSocket Push MQTT Topic Kitchen to Kitchen Notification Display (KDS) ↓ Update Device Trigger (Auto-prep items)

