### 4. Inventory Automation Flow
Daily Sales Data → AI Service → Demand Forecast → Low Stock Alerts ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ Historical Process with Generate Notify Sales Data ML Models Predictions → Auto-create & Alerts → PO → Google Sheets → ERP Integration

