### 5. AI Quality Detection Flow
Kitchen Camera → Computer Vision → Object Detection → Quality Analysis ↓ ↓ ↓ Process Image YOLOv8 Model Check: with OpenCV & CNN - Burnt food Classification - Portion size - Missing items ↓ Quality Score ↓ Feedback to Kitchen Staff Alert if Quality Issue Update Analytics

